ReS_JQIqB_I|Slyfer2812|Life is as inevitable as death.|"""What is there to fight for ? Life is a beautiful magnificient thing.""
I often sit on my own and question myself about death. About what's the point in the end. Someone very dear to  me passed away unexpectedly one day simply while falling

column2: no matter when or how It will happen. That scared me for a long time. Time passing faster  and faster as your life goes did not helped. But I realized something that is very obvious but opened up my eyes on life. If death is inevitable - So is life. Life is inevitable
column3: and this life is a one go. No going back. No second chance. One fucking shot at this. I felt different than most and lonely for almost all my life
column4: felt like I did not fit anywhere. Connecting to all of you with my videos changed me a lot. It taught me that you can do anything. Anything you want
column5: no matter how much you will fail at it before you get there. There's no losers. Tomorrow will be another day closer to the day we'll leave this earth.  Make the most of it.

Fashion Trends That Are Always Easy To Style | Fall 2023

Fashion trends come and go - we all know that - but there are some trends that just make sense to own. And when I say own I mean - own for the long haul. These are the trends that are actually not only easy to style but they work year after year. These are the fashion trends that you can incorporate into your outfits that will always make you look stylish and give your outfits a little extra something something. So today I wanted to focus on some key fall / winter 2023 fashion trends that will really stand the test of time. They are the ""practical"" trends that not only keep you looking good but also feeling good and these days that's super important to me too. What about you? Do you sacrifice comfort for style? I did this for years when I was younger but these days I absolutely won't wear something if it hurts me or is too tight or just doesn't sit right. Comfort is key for me but I'd love to know if you own any pieces that you will sacrifice your comfort for because they are just SO good. I'd love to know what they are in the comments below.

column1: Located at the center of the Mediterranean Sea
